00:28:39,988 --> 00:28:42,158
Terdapat perkataan "najis."

886
00:28:42,288 --> 00:28:43,987
- "Najis?" - Saya mendengar sesuatu seperti "byeon."

887
00:28:43,988 --> 00:28:44,988
Perkataan itu mestilah "alasan."

888
00:28:44,989 --> 00:28:48,758
